casebody.head_matter:
In the Matter of DISCIPLINE OF Donald B. TERRELL.
No. D-3024.
Supreme Court of the United States
April 2, 2018.
Donald B. Terrell, of Washington, District of Columbia, is suspended from the practice of law in this Court and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring him to show cause why he should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
